Kya aapke teeth crooked, spaced out ya overlap ho rahe hain?
Ya mirror mein smile dekhkar lagta hai ki confidence thoda kam ho gaya hai?
Agar haan, toh braces aapke liye ek safe aur effective solution ho sakte hain. 😊

Braces ek orthodontic treatment hota hai jo dheere-dheere teeth ko align karke aapki smile ko natural, balanced aur confident banata hai. Controlled aur gentle pressure ke through teeth ko unki correct position mein safely shift kiya jata hai.

Aaj ke time par braces ke multiple options available hain:
• Metal Braces – strong aur reliable
• Ceramic Braces – tooth-coloured, more aesthetic
• Self-Ligating Braces – faster results, less discomfort
• Clear Aligners – removable, almost invisible, lifestyle-friendly

Har patient ke liye best option unke teeth condition, age aur daily routine ke hisaab se decide kiya jata hai.
Isiliye treatment se pehle detailed dental check-up, photographs, X-rays aur digital scans zaroori hote hain, taaki treatment plan completely personalised ho. 🦷✨

Braces lagne ke baad shuru ke kuch din halka discomfort ho sakta hai, lekin mouth dheere-dheere adjust ho jata hai. Is dauraan proper oral hygiene maintain karna bahut important hota hai.

Treatment duration usually 12–18 months hota hai, case par depend karta hai.
Aur end result?
Ek straight, healthy aur confident smile — jo long-term confidence deta hai. 💙
